<div class="row">
  <div class="col-6">

    <h6 class="mb-3 fw-bold">
      Aspect Ratio / Preset
    </h6>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <div class="col-6 mt-2">
        <pre class="mt-0"><code>.ratio .700x1200</code></pre>
        <picture class="ratio ratio-3000x2250">
          <source srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0638/4637/products/DEB_BROWN_RUST_0680.jpg?v=1659112928&width=1140" media="all">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0638/4637/products/DEB_BROWN_RUST_0680.jpg?v=1659112928&width=1140">
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 mt-2">
        <pre class="mt-0 fs-sm tc">
        <code class="fs-sm fc-pink">
          $aspect-ratio-bg-svg: url('*');
        </code>
        </pre>
        <picture class="ratio ratio-3000x2250 bd">
          <img src="">
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="col-6">

    <h6 class="mb-3 fw-bold">
      Aspect Ratio / CSS Variable
    </h6>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <div class="col-6 mt-2">
        <picture class="ratio" style="--ratio: calc(800 / 1240)">
          <source srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0638/4637/files/WMN_3.jpg?v=1680442779" media="all">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0638/4637/files/WMN_3.jpg?v=1680442779">
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 mt-2">
        <picture class="ratio bd" style="--ratio: calc(800 / 1240)">
          <img src="">
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fs-sm py-2">
      In the above example we are setting the aspect ratio via the inline
      <code>
        style="*"
      </code>
      attribute. We pass a CSS variable and
      <code>
        calc()
      </code>
      function which
      will be digested by the
      <code>
        .ratio
      </code>
      class name. The
      <code>
        --ratio
      </code>
      variable requires height / width
      <code>
        calc(height / width)
      </code>
    </div>

<!-- esthetic-ignore-next -->
{% highlight html %}
<picture class="ratio" style="--ratio: calc(800 / 1240)">
  <source srcset="*" media="*">
  <img src="*">
</picture>
{% endhighlight %}

  </div>

  <div class="col-6 pl-3">
    <h6 class="my-2 fw-bold">
      No Placeholder
    </h6>
    Hide the background image placeholder SVG
    <div class="row ai-center mt-4">
      <div class="col-auto">
        <pre class="mt-0 fs-sm py-2 px-4">
        <code class="fs-sm">
          .ratio .no-placeholder
        </code>
        </pre>
        <pre class="mt-0 py-2 fs-sm px-4">
          <code class="fs-sm fc-pink">
            $aspect-ratio-bg-svg: null
          </code>
          </pre>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-0 fs-sm col-auto">
    <!-- esthetic-ignore-next -->
{% highlight html %}
<picture class="ratio no-placeholder">
</picture>
{% endhighlight %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>